DEBATR Frontend
DEBATR is a multi-page, visually engaging debate learning platform designed to help users understand and master the art of debating. This repository contains the frontend codebase built using React and Tailwind CSS, structured for modularity, responsiveness, and smooth user experience.

Features
Responsive multi-page layout with animated transitions

Sidebar navigation with a collapsible hamburger menu (hidden on the homepage)

Progress bar to track user advancement through lessons

Integrated content pages for topics such as motions, burdens, rebuttals, and more

Interactive quizzes and assessments

Badge and progress tracking

Tailwind CSS-based consistent theme across all pages

Clean, futuristic UI with animations using Framer Motion
